not paid when due.  Amounts due from You under this agreement may not be
withheld or offset by You against amounts due to You for any reason.  All fees
are payable in the currency of the United States of America. All fees
specifically exclude (and You are responsible for) any and all applicable
sales, use and other taxes, other than taxes based on Clustrix's income.

8.3. Changes to Fees. Clustrix may increase its annual subscription fees to
take effect for the upcoming Renewal Period, upon notice given at least 90
prior to the start of the upcoming next Renewal Period, which notice may be
provided by e-mail to Your email address.

8.4. Audit. During the term of this Agreement and for one (1) year thereafter,
Clustrix or its designated agent may inspect Your facilities and records to
